import React from 'react';
import './Location.css';
import Header from './Header';
import Footer from './Footer';
import Advertisement from './Advertisement';
import island from './island.jpeg';

const Location = () => {
    return (
      <div>
        <Header />
        <main>
        <Advertisement />
        <br></br>
        <div className="main-section">
            <img src={island} alt="Example Image" className="image" />
            <div className="text-container">
                <h2>Whispers of Love Peninsula</h2>
                <p>Congratulations on finding the perfect destination for your wedding! At Whispers of Love Peninsula, we believe that every love story deserves a breathtaking backdrop, and our island provides just that.

Imagine exchanging your vows amidst the gentle caress of ocean breezes, with stunning panoramic views of crystal-clear waters and sun-kissed shores. Whispers of Love Peninsula offers an enchanting setting that embraces the beauty of nature, creating an intimate and unforgettable experience for you and your loved ones.

Our peninsula is a secluded haven where love takes center stage. With its serene ambiance, lush greenery, and pristine beaches, it sets the stage for a romantic celebration. The tranquil sound of lapping waves and the whispering palm trees create a symphony of love, harmonizing with the promises you make to each other.

Our dedicated team is committed to ensuring that your special day is nothing short of perfection. From customized decor to exquisite cuisine, we will tailor every detail to reflect your unique love story. We understand the significance of this milestone, and we strive to create cherished memories that will last a lifetime.

Whispers of Love Peninsula is not just an island; it's a place where dreams come true, where love blossoms, and where lifelong commitments are sealed. It's a destination that celebrates the profound bond between two souls and offers an experience that goes beyond ordinary.

Choose Whispers of Love Peninsula for your wedding, and let the whispers of love guide you towards a day filled with joy, romance, and enchantment. Begin your journey as a married couple in a setting that embodies the very essence of love itself.

Welcome to Whispers of Love Peninsula, where your love story becomes an unforgettable reality.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </main>
        <Footer />
      </div>
    );
  };


export default Location;
